## Features

- **üîÑ All-or-nothing posting** - Automatic rollback on failures across all platforms
- **‚úÖ Pre-validation** - Fail fast with comprehensive error reporting before posting
- **üßµ Threading support** - Native threading on Twitter and Bluesky, numbered series on LinkedIn
- **üéØ Stateless operations** - No persistent state between calls, perfect for AI agents
- **üì± Media support** - Images, videos, documents with platform-specific validation
- **üõ°Ô∏è Robust error handling** - Detailed exception hierarchy with actionable guidance
- **üîå Unified interface** - Same `post()` and `post_thread()` methods across platforms
- **ü§ñ AI-agent optimized** - Simple, predictable API designed for automated usage

## Platform Support

| Platform | Single Posts | Threading | Media Support | Rate Limits |
|----------|--------------|-----------|---------------|-------------|
| **Twitter/X** | ‚úÖ | ‚úÖ Reply chains | Images, videos | 500 posts/month (free) |
| **Bluesky** | ‚úÖ | ‚úÖ AT Protocol | Images, videos | More permissive |
| **LinkedIn** | ‚úÖ | ‚ö†Ô∏è Numbered series* | Images, documents | 2s delays |
| **Reddit** | ‚úÖ | ‚ùå No threading | None (deprecated) | Standard API limits |

_*LinkedIn "threading" creates separate, unconnected posts with numbers - not true threads._

